      • AgGridColumn

        public AgGridColumn​(String headerName,
                    String field,
                    String type,
                    boolean hide,
                    boolean editable)
        Create a column header for a UI Ag Grid instance
        Parameters:
        headerName - String the text to display in the column header
        field - String the key to the row data
        type - String the type of column (date, text)
        hide - Boolean whether the column is visible or not
        editable - Boolean whether the contents of the cells in the column are editable.
